title: Wikipedia 07-2014 (EN) + Kiwix 0.9
description:
This is the torrent for the latest entire archive of Wikipedia to keep on your computer plus the Kiwix viewer software which works great for viewing the archive as well as any other html pages from other sites you have downloaded.

Perfect for having access to knowledge on nearly every subject without being dependent on the internet, while you're travelling, and if you somehow survived the apocalypse.

Good amount of torrent seeders with 1 web seed included which some clients can download from both at once for good speed
